c: 40
v: 5
t: "kdhdhabt qabl hwla' alkufaar qwm nuh wman tlahm min al'umam alty 'aelanat harbiha ealaa alrusul kead wthmwd, hayth eazamuu ealaa 'iydhayhm wtjmmaeu ealayhim baltedhyb 'aw alqtl, whmmat kulu 'umat min hadhih al'umam almkdhbt birasulihim lyqtlwh, wkhasmu balbatl; lybtlu bjdalhm alhaqu feaqabtuhm, fakayf kan eqaby 'iiahum eibratan llkhlq, wezt liman yati bedhm?"